name: Mohammad Patel
summary:
Mohammad Patel is a 31 year old South Asian man from Austin, Texas, currently living in Los Angeles. He is a Software Engineer, and an alumnus of the University of California, Berkeley. Mohammad is tall, standing at 6'1", and is quite active. His languages include English, Gujarati, and Hindi.

Principal in his life are honesty, hard work, and family. His leisure activities include hiking, video gaming, and reading. As a Muslim, he holds deep faith. Politically, he leans liberal.

Mohammad is looking for a woman between the ages of 25 and 35 who values an active lifestyle, does not drink or smoke, and wants children in the future, just like him. A fellow non-drinker and non-smoker would align well with him. His zodiac sign is Gemini and his personality type is INTJ. He currently has a pet cat and is open to welcoming more pets.
